  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub, not your words. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">Loaded every Climate TRACE industry emissions CSV into a single SQLite/Datasette instance with SpatiaLite. This enables arbitrary geospatial SQL, including bounding-box polygon queries across all emission assets, that the public API can't do.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A prototype visualization built on the Climate TRACE emissions data\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/climate-trace/prototype.png\" alt=\"A prototype visualization built on the Climate TRACE emissions data\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/climate-trace/prototype.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/climate-trace/prototype.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/climate-trace/prototype.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/climate-trace/prototype.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A prototype visualization built on the Climate TRACE emissions data\" width=\"2880\" height=\"1900\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.82deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2880×1900\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A prototype visualization built on the Climate TRACE emissions data</figcaption>\n</figure>",
